资源构建


对于YS库存、采购、制造等领域内的公共参照、过滤组件提供给其他各业务组的前端项目使用时，目前通过如下方式构建出对应js和css资源。


1.webpack.support.withReact.config.js（配置见下方）


var path = require('path');
var webpack = require('webpack');

//....

var config = {

 entry: { 'yxyweb-support-withReact': './mdfrefer.js' },
 mode: 'production',
 output: {
   //comments: false,
   publicPath: '../../',
   path: path.join(__dirname, 'static'),
   filename: 'public/javascripts/[name].min.js'
 },
  
 //....

 ],
 // 怎么配置的还是source-map
 devtool: 'source-map',
};
module.exports = config;


2.mdfrefer.js，内容参考如下：


//参照打包的入口文件
import '@mdf/theme-default/dist/filtercontainer';
import cb from '@mdf/cube/lib/cube';
const envConfig = require('./src/web/common/config.env').default;
if (process.env.__LANG__ && process.env.__LANG__ == true) {
  cb.lang.init({}, null);
  cb.lang.jsonp(0, 'YS_FED_FW,YS_SCM_STOCK,YS_FED_UIMG', envConfig.LANG_SERVERS_CENTRE, (data) => {
    //jsonp 多语回掉成功后函数

    // register businessContext
    const businessContext = require.context('business');
    cb.registerBusinessContext(businessContext)
    
    require('@yonyou/mdf-refer/lib/support_cb').default;
    console.log(" ************************报表多语加载!***************************");
  });
}


3.package.json的build命令加：npm run support:withReact



"support:withoutReact": "webpack --mode development --config webpack.support.withoutReact.config --colors --progress ",
"support:withReact": "webpack --mode development --config webpack.support.withReact.config --colors --progress ",
"support": "rimraf static && npm run support:withReact && npm run support:withoutReact ",


4.领域访问方式

统一通过： 业务前端域名/support/withReact 访问即可


@mdf/plugin-meta/src/controllers/support.js

import env from '../env';
const supportControler = {
  referUpdate: async function (ctx) {
    const isDev = process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development';
    const random = isDev ? '' : `?_=${env.STATIC_RANDOM_SUFFIX}`;
    const host = ctx.host;
    ctx.body = `(function () {
          let _origin = "http://"+"${host}";
          let _http=null;
          let _thirdsupport = document.getElementById("yxy-third-support");
          if(_thirdsupport){
            let _src = _thirdsupport ?_thirdsupport.getAttribute('src'):null;
            _origin = _src.includes('https') ? "https://" +"${host}":_origin
          }
          var script = document.createElement("script");
          var link = document.createElement("link");
          script.src = _origin+"/javascripts/yxyweb-support-${ctx.params.supportName}.min.js${random}";
          script.setAttribute("async", true);
          link.href = _origin+"/styles/default/yxyweb-support-${ctx.params.supportName}.min.css${random}";
          link.rel="stylesheet"
          link.type="text/css"
          let head = document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0];
          head.appendChild(script);
          head.appendChild(link);
          window.thirdsupportorigin = _origin;
        })()`
  }
}
export default supportControler;
